Dear God,
I just want to say THANK YOU; 
For giving my Son and I another shot at LIFE after 2022 tried everything physically and spiritually possible to dim our lights;  MERCY said NO!!!
No RIP, No SOS just VICTORY against all odds!!!!
if I start to talk we’ll most likely be on it all year long. 
But thank you God for fighting our battles, preserving our lives and most importantly blessing us with clear visions.. 
We Came, We Saw, We Conquered!!!
We return all the Glory to you GOD 🕊️
